<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background: #6772e5;
        color: white;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .content {
        background: #f9f9f9;
        padding: 20px;
        margin-top: 20px;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #666;
      }
      table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
      th {
        background: #6772e5;
        color: white;
        padding: 10px;
        text-align: left;
      }
      td {
        padding: 10px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
      }
      .total {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #6772e5;
        text-align: right;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .stripe-badge {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 15px;
      }
      .payment-info {
        background: #e8f4ff;
        padding: 15px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .secure-payment {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        margin-top: 15px;
      }
      .secure-payment img {
        height: 20px;
        margin-right: 10px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <h1>‚úÖ Pago Confirmado - Huellitas Pet</h1>
      </div>
      <div class='content'>
        <p>Hola <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,</p>
        <p>¬°Tu pago con Stripe ha sido
          <strong style='color: #6772e5;'>procesado exitosamente</strong>!</p>

        <div class='payment-info'>
          <p><strong>N√∫mero de orden:</strong> {{orderId}}</p>
          <p><strong>Fecha de pago:</strong> {{paymentDate}}</p>
        </div>

        <h3>Detalle de tu compra:</h3>
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Producto</th>
              <th style='text-align: center;'>Cantidad</th>
              <th style='text-align: right;'>Precio Unit.</th>
              <th style='text-align: right;'>Subtotal</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {{#each items}}
              <tr>
                <td>{{this.productName}}</td>
                <td style='text-align: center;'>{{this.quantity}}</td>
                <td style='text-align: right;'>${{this.unitPrice}}</td>
                <td style='text-align: right;'>${{this.subtotal}}</td>
              </tr>
            {{/each}}
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <div class='total'>
          Total: ${{total}}
        </div>

        <p style='margin-top: 30px;'>Tu pedido ser√° procesado y te contactaremos
          pronto para coordinar la entrega.</p>

        <div class='secure-payment'>
          <span>Pago procesado de forma segura por</span>
          <img
            src='https://cdn.worldvectorlogo.com/logos/stripe-2.svg'
            alt='Stripe'
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class='stripe-badge'>
        <img
          src='https://cdn.worldvectorlogo.com/logos/stripe-4.svg'
          alt='Powered by Stripe'
          width='120'
        />
      </div>

      <div class='footer'>
        <p>Este es un correo autom√°tico. Por favor no respondas a este mensaje.</p>
        <p>Huellitas Pet üêæ - Cuidamos de los que m√°s quer√©s</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>